  <Docs>
    <summary>Represents an override for a single color entry in a font’s color palette.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

<xref:T:SkiaSharp.SKFontPaletteOverride> is used with <xref:T:SkiaSharp.SKFontArguments> to replace specific entries in the color palette when cloning a typeface.

The <xref:P:SkiaSharp.SKFontPaletteOverride.Color> property stores a color in ARGB format (`0xAARRGGBB`), the same layout as <xref:T:SkiaSharp.SKColor>.
]]></format></remarks>
